        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "FLUX.2 Klein 4B BF16 is designed for environments where memory footprint and inference speed are critical. Its BF16 format reduces memory usage by half compared to FP32, while maintaining numerical stability for most tasks. When integrated into a multi-model API, it serves as an efficient component for handling specific workloads, such as lightweight inference or auxiliary processing, alongside larger models."
          }
