        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To incorporate FLUX.2 Klein 4B BF16 into your API stack, start by containerizing the model using Docker with a base image optimized for BF16 operations. Ensure your API gateway routes requests based on model capabilities—use load balancers to direct traffic to instances running this model for tasks like real-time text generation or embedding extraction. Implement health checks and versioning to manage updates seamlessly."
